<template>
  <v-container fluid class="d-inline-flex">
    <v-dialog
      v-model="dialog"
      max-width="1300"
      class="hDialog"
      >
      <template v-slot:activator="{ on, attrs }">
          <v-btn
            v-bind="attrs"
            v-on="on"
            color="primary"
            class="mx-3 font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
          >
          <v-icon
            left>
            mdi-pencil-plus-outline
          </v-icon>
            Przypisania Fibu
          </v-btn>
        </template>
          <DialogFibu />
    </v-dialog>

    <v-dialog
      v-model="dialog2"
      max-width="650">
      <template v-slot:activator="{ on, attrs }">
          <v-btn
          v-bind="attrs"
            v-on="on"
            color="teal"
            class="mr-2 font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
          >
          <v-icon
            left>
            mdi-microsoft-excel
          </v-icon>
            Raporty
          </v-btn>
      </template>
      <DialogReports />
    </v-dialog>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import DialogFibu from '../Dialogs/DialogFibu.vue';
import DialogReports from '../Dialogs/DialogReports.vue';

export default {
    data() {
        return {
            dialog: false,
            dialog2: false
        }
    },

    components: {
      DialogFibu,
      DialogReports
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
  .hDialog {
    min-height: 500px;
  }
</style>>
